1613
02:11:16.960 --> 02:11:19.079
-Why did you bring it to my brother?
-No. no. no.

1614
02:11:19.159 --> 02:11:22.079
Go. I will bring her.

1615
02:11:22.159 --> 02:11:23.640
No. No. No.

1616
02:11:24.920 --> 02:11:27.159
