1629
02:12:08.640 --> 02:12:11.880
-I will slaughter this man.
-[Mustapha] Exactly.

1630
02:12:14.520 --> 02:12:15.359
[Solomon] Lucas.

1631
02:12:17.359 --> 02:12:18.399
Lucas!

1632
02:12:19.560 --> 02:12:21.039
You tricked me.

1633
02:12:21.119 --> 02:12:23.800
