1634
02:12:26.800 --> 02:12:27.640
Lucas!

1635
02:12:30.960 --> 02:12:33.760
You used my daughter to pay off your debt?

1636
02:12:35.000 --> 02:12:36.840
Bro. go home. I'll fix this.

1637
02:12:38.119 --> 02:12:38.960
This is nothing.

1638
