1669
02:15:22.079 --> 02:15:23.039
[woman] That's very correct.

1670
02:15:24.239 --> 02:15:25.159
Derick.

1671
02:15:25.239 --> 02:15:28.840
How many days and hours
are equal to 200 hours?

1672
