1961.

1678
02:15:45.800 --> 02:15:46.880
[woman] That's correct.

1679
02:15:47.520 --> 02:15:48.359
False.

1680
02:15:49.159 --> 02:15:50.640
One hundred and eighty degrees.

1681
02:15:51.399 --> 02:15:52.279
True.

