1689
02:16:14.479 --> 02:16:18.960
True or false. The name "Teddy bear"
is used to describe a soft toy bear.

1690
02:16:19.520 --> 02:16:23.720
The name comes from
President Theodore "Teddy" Roosevelt.

1691
