1752
02:20:19.799 --> 02:20:21.520
Malala said. and I quote.

1753
02:20:22.719 --> 02:20:25.000
"There are two powers in this world."

1754
02:20:25.600 --> 02:20:26.440
"One.

1755
02:20:27.440 --> 02:20:28.680
is that of the sword.

1756
02:20:30.239 --> 02:20:31.079
the other.

1757
02:20:31.559 --> 02:20:32.399
the pen."

1758
02:20:33.159 --> 02:20:34.440
"There is a third power.

1759
02:20:35.159 --> 02:20:36.479
stronger than both."

1760
02:20:37.399 --> 02:20:39.000
"That of women."

1761
02:20:40.360 --> 02:20:44.440
Congratulations. Bodian Tech.
and happy graduation to all of you.

1762
02:20:45.479 --> 02:20:46.760
Thank you.

1763
02:20:46.840 --> 02:20:47.959
Thank you all.

1764
02:20:48.040 --> 02:20:48.959
Thank you.

1765
02:20:50.760 --> 02:20:52.639
Thank you. Happy graduation.

1766
02:20:53.600 --> 02:20:55.399
And see you on the other side.

